 Heartworms 推出强大的新单曲“Jacked”并宣布在英国举办亲密节目https://www.nme.com/news/music/heartworms-drop-powerful-new-single-jacked-and-announce-intimate-uk-shows-3764446?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=heartworms-drop-powerful-新单曲劫持并宣布亲密英国节目Poppy BurtonTue, 11 Jun 2024 15:06:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsNME RadarPost-Punkhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3764446 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="心丝虫" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “偏执狂梦想的配乐”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heartworms-drop-powerful-new-single-jacked-and-announce-intimate-uk-shows-3764446">Heartworms 发布了强大的新单曲“Jacked”并宣布亲密的英国节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="心丝虫" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heartworms-gilbert-trejo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heartworms">Heartworms</a>分享了她令人兴奋的新单曲“Jacked”，并宣布了三场亲密的英国演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/heartworms-a-comforting-notion-ep-review-radar-3417090">《Heartworms》——《安慰的想法》EP 评论：向下一个伟大的邪教乐队问好</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首新歌曲是这位伦敦艺术家自 2023 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-heartworms-new-single-may-i-comply-3532887">May I Comply</a> 》以来首次发行的歌曲，《May I Comply》取自广受好评的首张 EP《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/heartworms-a-comforting-notion-ep-review-radar-3417090">A Comforting Notion</a> 》。 Heartworms，真名 Jojo Orme，再次与长期合作者吉尔伯特·特雷霍 (Gilbert Trejo) 重聚，吉尔伯特·特雷霍还执导了《24 小时》和《May I Comply》的视频。</p><p>在讨论她对《Jacked》的愿景时，奥姆表示这首歌触及了“你正在逃避的黑暗或实体……但真正拥有它的是你。”</p><p>导演特雷霍表示，正因为如此，在视频中让奥姆“独自一人在世界上”以配合歌曲的世界末日基调至关重要。</p><p> “对我来说，”他说，“《Jacked》是偏执狂梦想的配乐”，他的视觉效果强化了“孤独和未知的感觉”，奥姆从一个神秘人物身边冲刺而去。</p><p> “乔乔和我知道我们在编写视频时需要传达这首歌的动感和能量，”他补充道。 “我们想让她飞起来，但她必须独自一人在这个世界上，所以我用安全别针将其他人的脸上的胶片乳剂刮掉。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Heartworms - Jacked（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mkXKgRtYp2U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>去年， <em>《NME》</em>在对 Orme 在伦敦 Village Underground 的头条秀<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/heartworms-live-in-london-village-underground-review-radar-3546575">进行现场回顾</a>时宣称“2024 年将属于 Heartworms”，而 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/heartworms-a-comforting-notion-ep-review-radar-3417090">首张 EP“Comforting Notion”则被誉为</a>“紧迫而重要，充满了下一个伟大作品的所有希望”。邪教行为”。</p><p> “Jacked”被戏称为今年晚些时候即将推出的更大项目的第一眼。</p><p> Heartworms 还宣布在伦敦的 Moth Club、布莱克浦的 Bootleg Social 和诺丁汉的 Bodega 举办一系列亲密演出。门票于 6 月 13 日星期四上午 9 点开始发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fheartworms-tickets%2Fartist%2F781327" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处购买门票</a>。请参阅下面她即将到来的完整巡演日期。</p><h2> <strong>Heartworms 即将到来的巡演日期是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>2024 年 7 月</strong></p><p><strong>12：格拉斯哥，TRNSMT 节</strong><br /><strong>13：诺丁汉，酒窖</strong><br /><strong>14：布莱克浦，盗版社交</strong><br /><strong>17：伦敦，飞蛾俱乐部</strong><br /><strong>28：牛津卡车节</strong></p><p><strong>2024 年 8 月</strong></p><p><strong>10：YPSIGROCK 节</strong><br /><strong>30：路的尽头</strong><br /><strong>31：曼彻斯特心理节</strong></p><p>在其他地方，Heartworms 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-announces-2024-uk-and-european-tour-with-heartworms-buy-tickets-3614666">在 St Vincent 的英国和欧洲巡演中进行了四场演出</a>，以支持她的第七张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/st-vincent-all-born-screaming-review-3749641">《All Born Screaming》，</a>并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kills">The Kills 进行了一系列北美演出。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heartworms-drop-powerful-new-single-jacked-and-announce-intimate-uk-shows-3764446">Heartworms 发布了强大的新单曲“Jacked”并宣布亲密的英国节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
